This deliverable was produced jointly by Princeton-PLI and Kitware as an AIQ-magnet integration for the Contextual Drag research program. It builds on infrastructure developed for the NeurIPS 2026 result-aggregation campaign and follows the package skeleton introduced in `princeton-pli/Contextual-Drag` PR #2.
